                <note rend="inline" type="source">511.4A6/375: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chairman of the American Delegation</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Caldwell</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-03T15:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 3, 1931—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>15. Your telegram 34, July 2, 10 a.m. Matter receiving consideration. Meanwhile
                    Department desires Delegation’s comment and recommendations.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Castle</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
